{"tid":765500,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友見到我素顏，佢講左一句...","createTime":"2018-08-02T21:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T13:54:39.000Z","uid":5770,"like":104,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9f3d159b27cc8842266f14ac8aaf1f93de0ee626","tid":765500,"uid":5770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T21:05:57.000Z","msg":"「喂你邊個！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n有日我沖完涼後，佢返到屋企時（有時會去佢屋企過夜），突然間冇哂表情，好嚴肅好惡好大聲咁問我，眼神好似見到個賊咁，我有一刻以為佢真係唔認得我，點知過左三秒佢就係到大笑，而我完全feel唔到好笑既地方，委屈到忍唔住滴左兩滴眼淚，佢即刻耍冧話玩下，但就令到我勁hurt，咁樣傷害自己女朋友好好玩咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d550665d9dea405e60ff5ffadbddc914439c96d","tid":765500,"uid":56544,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T21:09:25.000Z","msg":"又真係幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feabe12270617fd7313e2d161f5eaaf7e9fb2dd6","tid":765500,"uid":11893,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T21:10:51.000Z","msg":"玩下姐 咁都嬲"},{"pid":"00c39f7c3a2169e2b0a760c33c7202649cd8da0d","tid":765500,"uid":176168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T21:28:41.000Z","msg":"講笑姐"},{"pid":"3fadffe3e5ad1583d4c3ad7e9b60542ad369af99","tid":765500,"uid":108236,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T23:27:04.000Z","msg":"幾風趣 大家69 互射完就唔好再嬲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29515d1789577cf3f38486550d7d48cb0daee0c6","tid":765500,"uid":63588,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T23:30:55.000Z","msg":"男人老狗化咩妝"},{"pid":"9d097bcb0537aa513ace39a843919ed832e4c4c3","tid":765500,"uid":128928,"like":0,"dislik